00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,820
Quickly.

431
00:24:15,820 --> 00:24:17,920
Leave this place.

432
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:23,620
Gosh. All this hassle about ghosts!

433
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:26,920
What a waste of time!

